714
01:02:33,599 --> 01:02:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Učinimo to.

715
01:02:34,159 --> 01:02:34,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zabavimo se.

716
01:02:34,880 --> 01:02:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je sjajno.

717
01:02:36,079 --> 01:02:39,599
