724
01:03:05,679 --> 01:03:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] objavljujete ga tjedno.

725
01:03:07,519 --> 01:03:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] I kad god ste započeli, bilo je dvije osobe u epizodi.

726
01:03:11,519 --> 01:03:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] Problem, mislim da se tako zove.

727
01:03:13,360 --> 01:03:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] Problem, da, da.

728
01:03:14,239 --> 01:03:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali mislim da ste sada na ostali na jednom, ali i dalje je to prilično kratak videozapis.

729
01:03:19,360 --> 01:03:20,800
